edu.cpp.cs.cs141.prog_assgmnt_2.weapons

Class Weapon

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.prog_assgmnt_2.weapons.Weapon
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Pistol, Rifle, Shotgun

    public abstract class Weapon
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the base Weapon class for which all special weapon types are subclasses of. Base Weapon fields include the shared qualities of all special weapon types: damage, accuracy, ammo count, the name of the weapon, and whether or not it is loaded.
